reviews.review_text: Best sounding copy on IA The other reviews tell what needs telling about this wonderful show. Is it just me or is this the best sounding one? Lovely Touch as others have mentioned elsewhere.

Incredible Sound! As one who did not see the DEAD live nearly enough, I am closing that gap here on Internet Archive. I so much appreciate those who make it possible to enjoy programs such as this one. Thank You and God Bless
